  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"case-hero\" style=\"--case-bg: url(/precision/Medical_devices.jpg)\">\n<div class=\"container case-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"/\">首页</a><span>/</span><a href=\"/industries\">行业</a><span>/</span><a href=\"/industries/medical\">医疗器械</a><span>/</span><b>行业案例</b></div>\n<span>医疗器械案例</span>\n<h1>研发样件与定位治具试制</h1>\n<p>设备部件 / 测试夹具 / 非植入结构件</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section case-detail-section\">\n<div class=\"container case-detail-layout\">\n<article class=\"case-story\">\n<div class=\"case-summary-grid\">\n<div><span>行业</span><strong>医疗器械</strong></div>\n<div><span>零件功能</span><strong>设备部件 / 测试夹具 / 非植入结构件</strong></div>\n<div><span>制造能力</span><strong>CNC精密加工、工程塑料加工、不锈钢加工、尺寸报告</strong></div>\n</div>\n<h2>项目场景</h2>\n<p>围绕研发验证和装配定位，匹配材料、表面状态、清洁要求和包装方式。</p>\n<h2>方案配置</h2>\n<div class=\"case-step-grid\">\n<div><b>01</b><strong>零件功能确认</strong><span>明确装配位置、受力方式、环境条件和验证目标。</span></div>\n<div><b>02</b><strong>工艺与材料匹配</strong><span>根据尺寸、公差、表面和批次要求组合制造能力。</span></div>\n<div><b>03</b><strong>检测与交付</strong><span>围绕关键尺寸、外观状态和装配反馈输出交付资料。</span></div>\n</div>\n<h2>交付结果</h2>\n<p>样件、治具和尺寸记录同步交付，减少研发迭代中的重复沟通。</p>\n</article>\n<aside class=\"case-aside\">\n<img alt=\"研发样件与定位治具试制\" src=\"/precision/Medical_devices.jpg\"/>\n<h3>医疗器械制造能力</h3>\n<p>继续查看设备腔体、定位治具和研发样件等医疗器械制造案例。</p>\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/industries/medical\">返回医疗器械行业</a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/quote#quote-upload\">提交类似需求</a>\n</aside>\n</div>\n</section>\n"
